8949	[Right derived functors transport along a natural isomorphism]
8950	  \label{lem:rightDerivedNatIso}
8951	  \lean{AlgebraicGeometry.rightDerivedNatIso}
8952	  Let \(\mathcal{A}\) be an abelian category with enough injectives, \(\mathcal{B}\) abelian, and
8953	  \(F, G : \mathcal{A} \to \mathcal{B}\) additive functors. A natural isomorphism \(F \cong G\)
8954	  induces, for every \(n\), a natural isomorphism of right derived functors
8955	  \[
8956	    F.\mathrm{rightDerived}\,n \;\cong\; G.\mathrm{rightDerived}\,n.
8957	  \]

